long.am,ar,bg,bn,ca,cs,da,de,el,en,en_AU,en_G:
"Moshaveran-REST" shows swagger yaml/json rendered by Swagger-UI so fast.
This extension replaces swagger json into preview html include bearer Authentication.
Works offline and you can connect it to the localhost. The new version of swagger doesn't support .net framework. But if you want to experience new version of the swagger on the old version, just install this extension and don't be hesitate.
